TITLE: Creating a Highlighter Instance
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating a reusable highlighter instance with specific theme and language.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shikijs/shiki/blob/main/docs/guide/install.md#2025-04-15_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { createHighlighter } from 'shiki'

const highlighter = await createHighlighter({
  themes: ['nord'],
  langs: ['javascript'],
})

const code = highlighter.codeToHtml('const a = 1', {
  lang: 'javascript',
  theme: 'nord'
})
```

