TITLE: Basic HTML Generation with Shiki
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the codeToHtml shorthand function to generate highlighted HTML from JavaScript code.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shikijs/shiki/blob/main/docs/guide/install.md#2025-04-15_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { codeToHtml } from 'shiki'

const code = 'const a = 1' // input code
const html = await codeToHtml(code, {
  lang: 'javascript',
  theme: 'vitesse-dark'
})

console.log(html) // highlighted html string
```

