TITLE: Converting Code to HAST using Shiki Highlighter
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to create a Shiki highlighter and convert code to HAST format. The highlighter is configured with Nord and Min-light themes, supporting JavaScript language.
SOURCE: https://github.com/shikijs/shiki/blob/main/docs/api.md#2025-04-15_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { createHighlighter } from 'shiki'

const highlighter = await createHighlighter({
  themes: ['nord', 'min-light'],
  langs: ['javascript'],
})
// ---cut---
const root = highlighter.codeToHast(
  'const a = 1',
  { lang: 'javascript', theme: 'nord' }
)

console.log(root)
```

